        <h3 class="hed">The Enduring Myth of Black Criminality</h3>
    </a>
    <ul class="metadata">
        <li class="byline"><a href="/author/ta-nehisi-coates/" title="Ta-Nehisi Coates">Ta-Nehisi Coates</a> and <a href="/author/jackie-lay/" title="Jackie Lay">Jackie Lay</a></li>
